{"tid":1859010,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【支那狗畜生蝗蟲垃圾廢物發威威】 中國留學生扮港人入境　獲澳洲海關放行","createTime":"2020-02-03T04:36:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T04:47:28.000Z","uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8268e04d1e003b1a322193e321defb751e0660cd","tid":1859010,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:36:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/d/d5/11-24_21-09-28.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20101124165600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fd%2Fd5%2F11-24_21-09-28.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20101124165600&h=7502298d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/8c3/ea7/8c3ea70ca63b1e8870d4e3a2ae200e296d16dced_n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2F8c3%2Fea7%2F8c3ea70ca63b1e8870d4e3a2ae200e296d16dced_n.png&h=fdf53a9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/d57/631/d57631f406306ba3cea5831708febd9cf8e9af3b_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2Fd57%2F631%2Fd57631f406306ba3cea5831708febd9cf8e9af3b_n.jpg&h=f5ceb32b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n澳洲政府因應武漢肺炎疫情，上週六（1日）宣佈禁止非公民、永久居民及其直系親屬入境，大批中國留學生受影響。澳媒報導，一名中國留學生經香港轉機返回澳洲昆士蘭，過關前將入境登記卡的出境地改為香港，結果成功獲澳洲海關放行。<br />\n<br />\n該名化名小K的留學生透露，他在禁令生效當晚11時許抵達布里斯班，落機後才得知消息。小K的同學甚至傳送訊息，嘲笑他將要被遣返；惟他臨急生智，將入境登記卡上的「CHINA」劃掉並改為「HONG KONG」，結果關員只看了他一眼，便允許他從另一側通道入境，連行李都沒有檢查。<br />\n<br />\n其他受訪的留學生則運氣較差，同樣在昆士蘭讀書的小輝，當日從上海啟程並經香港轉機到布里斯班，在落地前1小時澳洲政府才宣佈限制令。惟小輝經轉機抵達，而行李卻直達澳洲，無法入境的情況下無法取回行李。小輝與幾名同胞最後被海關帶進「小黑屋」，在對方要求下即場購票返程，再由航空公司轉運行李。"},{"pid":"2079078fda217ca697c1c1e2872c998e090d3111","tid":1859010,"uid":319606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:40:20.000Z","msg":"【撐醫護】屌打撕紙狗！全港最大連儂牆正式上線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1859012\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1859012</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"76fd0e3afd0e8deb15e5997ff325739c474e16f8","tid":1859010,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:40:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-7585bcc3997e85632eb7f7d9f9ccb608_hd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic1.zhimg.com%2F50%2Fv2-7585bcc3997e85632eb7f7d9f9ccb608_hd.jpg&h=406c6614&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2b908d48b40a94e6acfafff51ef8a066767d4bb2","tid":1859010,"uid":167928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:47:05.000Z","msg":"全盛時期 金剛同陳啓泰1日要出現幾多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8849ef2ae4f199bb21a18d0b75802b201f6c95d0","tid":1859010,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2b908d48b40a94e6acfafff51ef8a066767d4bb2","tid":1859010,"uid":167928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:47:05.000Z","msg":"全盛時期 金剛同陳啓泰1日要出現幾多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:47:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}